 <h2 class="about-page__headline">Welcome to the <span class="transformed transformed--red">JS Tasker</span> Web Application</h2>
        <p class="about-page__paragraph">
            <span class="transformed transformed--red">JS Tasker</span> is a web application whose main purpose is to provide a platform for users to practice their javascript knowledge.
            <span class="transformed transformed--red">JS Tasker</span> serves its users with a single javascript task which is generated by our sophisticated task parsing tool. Every task is a random one!
            Users must guess the <span class="transformed transformed--red">console.log</span> output of the task and they get points based on their answer. Users can then track their progress,statistics and history on the profile page. Task levels are at random as well, meaning <span class="transformed transformed--red">JS Tasker</span> assumes
            that the user's knowledge of a javascript language is already high! You can read more about <span class="transformed transformed--red">JS Tasker</span> technical details on our <a href="#"><span class="transformed transformed--yellow">GitHub page.</span></a> 
